song.title: HOLY
song.lyrics:
Holy, holy, holy, Lord, God of Hosts! Holy, holy, holy, Lord, God of Hosts!
Heaven and earth are full of your glory! Hosanna in the highest. Hosanna in the highest. Hosanna in the highest. Hosanna in the highest.
Blessed is he who comes in the name of th Lord! Hosanna in the highest. Hosanna in the highest. Hosanna in the highest. Hosanna in the highest.
